I've never seen anything
like them before.

14
00:01:15,859 --> 00:01:17,959
They're from somewhere far away.

15
00:01:20,207 --> 00:01:21,455
I don't have any money.

16
00:01:21,868 --> 00:01:24,375
That's okay. I'm gonna give you
one of these anyway.

17
00:01:29,845 --> 00:01:30,845
There.

18
00:01:31,466 --> 00:01:32,633
That's great.

19
00:01:34,303 --> 00:01:35,303
Thank you.

20
