Morning.

35
00:03:30,544 --> 00:03:32,294
Good morning, funny face.

36
00:03:32,921 --> 00:03:34,521
You ready for our day?

37
00:03:36,285 --> 00:03:38,008
This is the map Mom left for us.

38
00:03:38,403 --> 00:03:40,303
There's four rollercoasters.

39
00:03:40,874 --> 00:03:44,017
We agreed. No rollercoasters.
You can go on any other ride you like,

40
00:03:44,142 --> 00:03:47,114
