- Yeah.

289
00:19:53,808 --> 00:19:55,040
For the weekend.

290
00:19:55,589 --> 00:19:56,444
And?

291
00:19:57,184 --> 00:19:58,112
And what?

292
00:19:58,280 --> 00:20:00,615
