and then dinner after.

296
00:20:10,505 --> 00:20:13,484
She was completely understanding
when I told her that I had to work.

297
00:20:22,121 --> 00:20:25,230
When my mom took me
to my first movie when I was six,

298
00:20:25,865 --> 00:20:27,336
I was so excited.

299
00:20:27,461 --> 00:20:29,503
She bought me a box
of popcorn, and...

300
00:20:29,628 --> 00:20:30,774
