319
00:21:20,704 --> 00:21:21,946
Flight 821.

320
00:21:22,450 --> 00:21:23,574
Boston to Rome.

321
00:21:24,926 --> 00:21:26,907
She was supposed
to be on that flight.

322
00:21:27,161 --> 00:21:28,774
<i>Rescue teams and divers</i>

323
00:21:28,899 --> 00:21:30,494
<i>continue to scour the wreckage.</i>

324
00:21:30,619 --> 00:21:32,392
<i>We will continue</i>
<i>to bring you live coverage</i>

325
00:21:32,517 --> 00:21:34,910
<i>of this disaster as it comes</i>
<i>across our desk.</i>

326
00:21:35,035 --> 00:21:36,641
<i>Representatives of Tropos Air...</i>

327
00:21:36,766 --> 00:21:38,347
You were going to die.

328
00:21:39,006 --> 00:21:41,802
<i>We will bring you live coverage</i>
<i>just as soon as it happens.</i>

329
00:21:41,927 --> 00:21:43,285
<i>Right now, what you're...</i>

330
00:21:43,410 --> 00:21:44,547
I saved you.

331
00:21:45,747 --> 00:21:46,890
How did you...

332
00:21:50,403 --> 00:21:52,085
You're not safe. Yet.

333
00:21:54,838 --> 00:21:56,522
There is something I need to do.

334
00:21:58,738 --> 00:22:00,012
I have to go out.

335
00:22:01,269 --> 00:22:03,376
I would prefer not to gag you.

336
00:22:07,289 --> 00:22:09,186
But it is for your own protection.

337
00:22:24,864 --> 00:22:25,877
What if he did?

338
00:22:26,002 --> 00:22:28,817
I mean, what if he somehow
knew the plane was gonna crash?

339
00:22:28,942 --> 00:22:30,625
So you think this Brandon guy
was right?

340
00:22:30,750 --> 00:22:32,711
That they can see the events
before they happen.

341
00:22:32,836 --> 00:22:34,811
I'm sorry, what plane crash?

342
00:22:35,248 --> 00:22:37,153
Christine Hollis was supposed
to be on a plane

343
00:22:37,278 --> 00:22:38,988
that crashed just off
the coast of Italy.

344
00:22:39,113 --> 00:22:41,133
- 200 people were killed.
- Oh, dear.

345
00:22:41,258 --> 00:22:43,384
I mean, what if he wasn't
trying to kidnap her?

346
00:22:43,509 --> 00:22:45,311
What if he was trying
to save her life?

347
00:22:45,436 --> 00:22:47,563
What is so special about her?
Why save her?

348
00:22:47,688 --> 00:22:49,508
Why did one of them save us?

349
00:22:51,437 --> 00:22:54,191
I've got the results of the blood
sample from the book.

350
00:22:58,225 --> 00:23:00,920
High concentration of Capsaicin.

351
00:23:01,718 --> 00:23:03,766
Which means it's not blood at all,

352
00:23:03,891 --> 00:23:05,731
it's chili pepper juice.

353
00:23:05,856 --> 00:23:07,856
He must have spilled some
in the book.

354
00:23:07,981 --> 00:23:10,688
Well, that's great news.
So we'll add "messy" to the APB.

355
00:23:11,225 --> 00:23:13,091
No, it is good news.

356
00:23:13,841 --> 00:23:17,417
Concentration at 970,000
on the Scoville scale,

357
00:23:18,120 --> 00:23:21,041
that's one of the hottest
chili peppers there is.

358
00:23:21,166 --> 00:23:24,972
I hypothesize a Naga Jolokia
from India,

359
00:23:25,541 --> 00:23:28,150
otherwise known as
the King Cobra chili.

360
00:23:28,708 --> 00:23:30,177
I once ate one.

361
00:23:31,272 --> 00:23:33,578
The flatulence was horrible.

362
00:23:33,854 --> 00:23:35,288
Very embarrassing.

363
00:23:36,952 --> 00:23:38,802
Are these peppers sold in Boston?

364
00:23:38,927 --> 00:23:40,511
Oh, I... I imagine so.

365
00:23:40,636 --> 00:23:43,265
Though I don't suspect
one could grow them here.

366
00:23:44,705 --> 00:23:45,511
Astrid?

367
00:23:45,636 --> 00:23:48,509
Locate anyone who's importing
those peppers locally. Got it.

368
00:23:55,055 --> 00:23:55,941
Well.

369
00:23:56,674 --> 00:23:58,456
It appears you've been busy.

370
00:24:06,785 --> 00:24:09,342
Your actions took us all
by surprise.

371
00:24:10,561 --> 00:24:13,640
I take it you've come here
to explain yourself.

372
00:24:14,912 --> 00:24:16,954
Then you are aware
of the plane crash.

373
00:24:17,122 --> 00:24:18,122
Of course.

374
00:24:19,939 --> 00:24:21,289
Christine Hollis.

375
00:24:21,981 --> 00:24:23,031
Who is she?

376
00:24:24,800 --> 00:24:27,750
I have observed this woman
for much of her life.

377
00:24:28,542 --> 00:24:29,759
She is unique.

378
00:24:30,049 --> 00:24:31,549
They are all unique.

379
00:24:32,640 --> 00:24:34,263
That is not reason to interfere

380
00:24:34,431 --> 00:24:36,891
