was meant to take.

381
00:24:37,328 --> 00:24:39,060
We have interfered before.

382
00:24:41,146 --> 00:24:43,896
Only to correct a mistake
of our own making.

383
00:24:44,926 --> 00:24:46,535
She has no future.

384
00:24:47,036 --> 00:24:48,402
Then why do I see it?

385
00:24:51,934 --> 00:24:54,184
Why do I see that she is important?

386
00:24:56,371 --> 00:24:58,645
Your perception must be in error.

387
00:25:05,042 --> 00:25:06,042
Perhaps.

388
00:25:07,305 --> 00:25:09,405
Your oversight will be forgiven,

389
00:25:10,065 --> 00:25:12,440
but Miss Hollis must be corrected.

390
00:25:13,305 --> 00:25:15,055
We've already seen to it.

391
00:25:17,672 --> 00:25:19,726
- You should eat something.
- Thanks.

392
00:25:19,851 --> 00:25:22,933
If there's something significant
about this girl, I just don't see it.

393
00:25:23,058 --> 00:25:25,918
After her parents died, she was
taken in by her mother's best friend,

394
00:25:26,043 --> 00:25:30,047
who was a veterinarian in Worcester.
She got decent grades in college and

395
00:25:30,502 --> 00:25:34,078
interned at art galleries in the summer.
I think she's just like anyone else.

396
00:25:34,203 --> 00:25:35,992
Guys? I think I found something.

397
00:25:36,401 --> 00:25:38,162
There's King Cobra chilis.

398
00:25:38,287 --> 00:25:41,706
Three Boston restaurants imported them
last year, and one private citizen.

399
00:25:41,994 --> 00:25:43,300
- Who?
- I don't know.

400
00:25:43,425 --> 00:25:45,918
He paid with a money order.
But we have an address.

401
00:25:46,086 --> 00:25:49,145
- It's an apartment in Cambridge.
- Can you give the address to Broyles

402
00:25:49,270 --> 00:25:52,460
and get him to have a back-up team
standing by in case we need them?

403
00:25:52,585 --> 00:25:53,635
Sure thing.

404
00:25:58,285 --> 00:25:59,632
Taste this, please.

405
00:26:04,761 --> 00:26:06,770
No. That's what I was afraid of.

406
00:26:07,457 --> 00:26:08,562
What is that?

407
00:26:08,687 --> 00:26:10,651
French vanilla ice cream
and cough syrup.

408
00:26:12,017 --> 00:26:15,088
I suspect that this...
The secret ingredient

409
00:26:15,213 --> 00:26:18,111
