have any fresh cherries.

410
00:26:19,114 --> 00:26:22,025
Unless you'd make a trip
to the market.

411
00:26:22,448 --> 00:26:25,422
If I do, I am no longer
your taste tester.

412
00:26:26,338 --> 00:26:27,338
Deal.

413
00:27:43,592 --> 00:27:45,042
You got my message.

414
00:27:49,938 --> 00:27:52,625
I suspected that a likeness
of a nitrogen molecule

415
00:27:52,750 --> 00:27:54,539
would attract your attention.

416
00:27:55,877 --> 00:27:57,627
Please don't take my son.

417
00:28:03,178 --> 00:28:05,128
Your friend and I had a deal.

418
00:28:05,868 --> 00:28:07,468
We had an arrangement.

419
00:28:11,321 --> 00:28:13,399
I know what I did was wrong, but...

420
00:28:13,721 --> 00:28:15,821
That is not why I contacted you.

421
00:28:17,322 --> 00:28:19,265
I need your help.

422
00:28:20,010 --> 00:28:21,010
My help?

423
00:28:27,298 --> 00:28:29,398
In that case, I should call him.

424
00:28:30,512 --> 00:28:31,862
And Agent Dunham.

425
00:28:32,157 --> 00:28:34,378
They'll want to know
I'm talking to you.

426
00:28:34,546 --> 00:28:37,895
I suspect that they might be
occupied right now.

427
00:29:35,588 --> 00:29:36,788
On your knees.

428
00:29:37,823 --> 00:29:39,273
Down on the ground.

429
00:29:41,952 --> 00:29:43,102
Take it easy.

