00:29:44,279 --> 00:29:45,429
Take it easy.

431
00:29:47,283 --> 00:29:48,433
Take it easy.

432
00:30:07,630 --> 00:30:09,780
What is it that requires my help?

433
00:30:12,445 --> 00:30:15,495
I have interfered
in the natural course of events.

434
00:30:16,504 --> 00:30:17,804
To correct that,

435
00:30:18,307 --> 00:30:21,213
the others will try to kill
Christine Hollis

436
00:30:21,819 --> 00:30:23,269
until they succeed.

437
00:30:24,645 --> 00:30:26,772
If we run, they will find us.

438
00:30:27,413 --> 00:30:30,202
If I stop the assassin,
they will send another.

439
00:30:31,682 --> 00:30:34,208
I cannot see any course of action

440
00:30:34,661 --> 00:30:36,161
that will prevent...

441
00:30:37,757 --> 00:30:38,757
her death.

442
00:30:40,708 --> 00:30:42,256
What makes you think I can help?

443
00:30:42,605 --> 00:30:45,111
Because you have solved
such a matter before.

444
00:30:46,068 --> 00:30:48,929
You saw beyond the limitations
of your problems.

445
00:30:49,481 --> 00:30:50,531
Not really.

446
00:30:51,775 --> 00:30:53,325
I just missed my son.

447
00:30:57,017 --> 00:31:00,816
May I ask what is so important
about Miss Hollis?

448
00:31:04,915 --> 00:31:06,815
I cannot explain the reason.

449
00:31:08,230 --> 00:31:09,760
I merely see it.

450
00:31:12,192 --> 00:31:14,292
I have never experienced such...

451
