452
00:31:18,261 --> 00:31:19,511
But the others,

453
00:31:19,636 --> 00:31:21,545
they say she is of no consequence.

454
00:31:23,648 --> 00:31:24,798
In that case,

455
00:31:25,141 --> 00:31:28,391
if you can not persuade
the others of your conviction,

456
00:31:29,040 --> 00:31:31,096
then you must do something
to prove it.

457
00:31:32,767 --> 00:31:34,885
You must make her important.

458
00:31:38,346 --> 00:31:40,346
And of course whatever you do,

459
00:31:41,614 --> 00:31:44,574
