474
00:33:05,947 --> 00:33:06,947
exactly...

475
00:33:08,820 --> 00:33:09,820
as I say.

476
00:33:17,025 --> 00:33:18,025
Any ideas?

477
00:33:19,529 --> 00:33:21,248
What are they looking for?

478
00:33:21,970 --> 00:33:24,835
We're looking for them but
