479
00:33:25,003 --> 00:33:27,253
That's why they keep on showing up.

480
00:33:27,589 --> 00:33:29,256
So what are they looking for?

481
00:33:32,898 --> 00:33:33,898
Where?

482
00:33:34,513 --> 00:33:37,001
Someone just called in a description
of our second Observer.

483
00:33:37,126 --> 00:33:39,016
He was spotted at a motel in Lowell.

484
00:34:40,078 --> 00:34:41,203
What are you doing?

485
00:34:41,924 --> 00:34:43,474
Tell me where she is.

486
00:34:43,790 --> 00:34:45,332
Just tell me where she is.

487
00:34:45,542 --> 00:34:48,585
You know I'm just trying to do my job.
I have no quarrel with you.

488
00:34:52,340 --> 00:34:53,590
Are you insane?

489
00:34:54,090 --> 00:34:55,090
Good-bye.

490
00:36:30,133 --> 00:36:31,483
Christine Hollis?

491
00:36:54,762 --> 00:36:56,462
I'm Agent Olivia Dunham.

492
00:36:56,651 --> 00:36:58,001
I'm with the FBI.

493
00:36:58,218 --> 00:36:59,918
It's gonna be all right.

494
00:37:02,034 --> 00:37:03,387
What about the man?

495
00:37:04,634 --> 00:37:06,134
The one who took me?

496
00:37:09,186 --> 00:37:10,636
Let's get you home.

497
00:37:19,455 --> 00:37:21,671
Will she be safe now?

498
00:37:24,255 --> 00:37:25,305
Who is she?

499
00:37:26,899 --> 00:37:28,449
